Introduction

SongCryGirlz (Korean: 송크라이걸즈; Japanese:ソンクライガールズ) was a South Korean girl group under Sunflower Republic 91 whose last line-up consisted of Jisoo, Suseong and JuA.

The group debuted on May 17, 2010 with the single album 사랑노래 (featuring SongCry and Minji) and disbanded in 2015.
